46
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:09,520
- Hello.
- Hello.

47
00:04:10,090 --> 00:04:11,319
Why are you here?

48
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:14,030
We came to watch a movie.
I didn't have any popcorn.

49
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:16,889
But still. At this hour?
Without telling me?

50
