55
00:04:29,269 --> 00:04:31,040
- That's my jacket.
- No, I got this.

56
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,139
- You have makeup on.
- No.

57
00:04:32,139 --> 00:04:33,680
My... My movie is about...

58
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,350
Guess who?

59
00:04:39,149 --> 00:04:40,149
Jo Il Kwon?

60
00:04:42,689 --> 00:04:43,889
Hello.

61
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,959
