73
00:05:29,670 --> 00:05:32,439
- I'm so proud of you, Ha Kyung.
- Stop it.

74
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:35,040
Great job.

75
00:05:35,269 --> 00:05:37,740
Try to work things out.
Mr. Jo is a great guy.

76
