I heard you say that too.

100
00:06:40,339 --> 00:06:42,139
We're like family?

101
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,910
I didn't know
you thought of me like that.

102
00:06:44,910 --> 00:06:46,579
Right.

103
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:48,649
This is so uncanny.

104
00:06:49,009 --> 00:06:51,519
