Eat up.

107
00:06:57,189 --> 00:06:58,189
Ha Kyung.

108
00:06:58,790 --> 00:06:59,860
Open your mouth.

109
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,529
I'll feed myself.

110
00:07:05,529 --> 00:07:08,399
Come on.
Wait, it's falling. It's falling.

111
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,370
- It's good.
- Is it?

112
00:07:14,370 --> 00:07:16,139
- Thank you.
- Sure.

113
00:07:19,939 --> 00:07:21,949
What? Do I have
something on my face?

114
00:07:23,410 --> 00:07:26,379
Do you really have no idea,
or are you asking me to test you?

115
00:07:31,019 --> 00:07:32,019
Well...

116
00:08:23,139 --> 00:08:25,410
Don't they look so good together?

117
