"A man was charged for murder..."

126
00:09:10,549 --> 00:09:11,559
Hello.

127
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:12,690
- Hello.
- Hello.

128
00:09:12,690 --> 00:09:13,990
Hello.

129
00:09:13,990 --> 00:09:15,159
Nice to meet you.

130
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:16,360
I came here because...

131
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:18,399
I wanted to talk
about today's interview briefly.

132
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:23,070
What is it?
Why did you suddenly smile?

133
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:25,039
I was just reminded of that time...

134
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:27,240
when I had first met
Anchor Lee in this room.

135
00:09:28,169 --> 00:09:31,980
Back then, I was worried sick
that he'd criticize you so much.

136
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,309
But now...

137
00:09:34,879 --> 00:09:35,950
"But now"?

138
00:09:40,179 --> 00:09:42,519
- I guess you could say that.
- Silence.

139
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:43,850
Silence. I need to film soon.

140
00:09:43,850 --> 00:09:45,820
I'm glad you're not nervous.

141
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:49,360
This is just a test, so relax, okay?

142
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,830
Okay.

143
00:09:50,830 --> 00:09:52,259
Let me see how much time you have.

144
00:09:52,259 --> 00:09:53,299
Okay.

145
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:54,570
