who have been job hunting.

156
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:40,879
Cut! Ha Jin, you've improved
so much.

157
00:10:41,450 --> 00:10:44,519
Really? Can I try it again?

158
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:46,679
I think I sped up a bit at the end.

159
00:10:46,820 --> 00:10:49,720
I didn't notice that, but okay.

160
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,389
- Let me know when you're ready.
- Okay.

161
00:10:51,389 --> 00:10:54,789
Could you take one from the front?

162
