199
00:13:26,879 --> 00:13:28,909
Live an honest life from now on.

200
00:13:28,909 --> 00:13:31,649
Think of your mother, okay?

201
00:13:31,750 --> 00:13:32,850
Thank you.

202
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,720
And I'm truly sorry.

203
00:13:37,789 --> 00:13:38,789
See you tomorrow.

204
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:42,330
- What?
- Don't you have a debt to pay?

205
