Will you really be all right?

211
00:14:04,179 --> 00:14:06,779
I gave this a lot of thought.

212
00:14:06,820 --> 00:14:08,750
But I'll regret it
if I don't do this.

213
00:14:08,950 --> 00:14:14,230
Okay. I know that
he apologized countless times,

214
00:14:14,230 --> 00:14:16,460
but I don't think
he should work with you.

215
00:14:17,059 --> 00:14:19,330
I'm going to make him do
office work.

216
00:14:19,899 --> 00:14:22,000
Thank you for allowing this.

217
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:24,269
