218
00:14:24,269 --> 00:14:25,899
You'll be blessed.

219
00:14:26,039 --> 00:14:28,110
People have said that
I look nicer now.

220
00:14:28,110 --> 00:14:29,639
I no longer look like a villainess.

221
00:14:29,639 --> 00:14:32,639
It's true. Now, you just need
to become the national anchor.

222
00:14:32,639 --> 00:14:35,409
Let's do well and hit the jackpot.

223
00:14:38,950 --> 00:14:40,120
What is it?

224
00:14:40,179 --> 00:14:44,620
Anchor Lee Jeong Hoon's
doctor called.

225
00:14:44,620 --> 00:14:47,590
He wanted your number.

226
00:14:47,889 --> 00:14:49,629
His doctor?

227
00:14:49,629 --> 00:14:50,629
Yes.

228
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:54,129
(Seoseong University,
Professor Yoo Sung Hyuk)

229
00:15:09,549 --> 00:15:11,149
Hello, sit down.

230
00:15:12,019 --> 00:15:13,149
Hello.

231
00:15:15,690 --> 00:15:18,690
You must've been puzzled
that I wanted to see you.

232
00:15:19,690 --> 00:15:23,559
It's fine.
I've read your thesis before.

233
00:15:23,690 --> 00:15:26,730
