about Jeong Hoon's illness.

234
00:15:27,769 --> 00:15:28,799
I do.

235
00:15:29,730 --> 00:15:32,740
Why did you want to see me?

236
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:34,409
Is he okay?

237
00:15:34,409 --> 00:15:36,139
Yes, he is.

238
00:15:36,370 --> 00:15:39,409
I just thought it'd be nice
to meet you once.

239
00:15:41,179 --> 00:15:43,049
I'm relieved. I was worried.

240
00:15:46,679 --> 00:15:48,019
As his doctor,

241
00:15:48,019 --> 00:15:52,590
I know every little thing about him.

242
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:57,389
