about you.

243
00:15:58,200 --> 00:16:00,100
I only recently found out...

244
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:01,929
that you two
were in a serious relationship.

245
00:16:02,529 --> 00:16:06,039
We've only recently become serious.

246
00:16:07,570 --> 00:16:10,210
So it wasn't a serious relationship
from the beginning.

247
00:16:10,210 --> 00:16:13,480
Is it true that you were dating
when those scandals came out?

248
00:16:15,679 --> 00:16:17,450
If you're worried
about your privacy being exposed,

249
00:16:17,450 --> 00:16:19,019
there's no need to be.

250
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:22,820
- Okay.
- How much do you know...

251
00:16:22,820 --> 00:16:25,820
about his illness?

252
00:16:26,059 --> 00:16:28,960
I just know that
he's suffering from hyperthymesia.

253
00:16:29,460 --> 00:16:31,929
