254
00:16:32,159 --> 00:16:35,669
Then I won't need
to explain what it is.

255
00:16:37,740 --> 00:16:39,139
What about him?

256
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:43,309
What do you mean?

257
00:16:43,669 --> 00:16:45,279
For example,

258
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:50,580
did you know that his ex had died?

259
00:16:53,549 --> 00:16:54,549
