260
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:57,549
I guess you didn't know.

261
00:16:58,919 --> 00:17:01,490
She was murdered by her stalker.

262
00:17:01,490 --> 00:17:02,960
She met a gruesome death.

263
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:08,900
Since you said you two
were in a serious relationship,

264
00:17:08,900 --> 00:17:11,940
